commands.respawn: {alias={'re','reset','respawn','rf'},onExecution=function(self,message)local plr=message and getplayermatchingstring(message) or self plr:LoadCharacter()end,}
commands.kick: {alias={'kick','k','remove'},onExecution=function(self,message) local plr=message and getplayermatchingstring(message) or nil if plr then plr:kick() end end,}
commands.shutdown: {alias={'shutdown','sd'},onExecution=function(self,...) local args=table.pack(...) message='' for _,v in pairs(args) do message=message..' '..v end message=message:sub(0,-3) game:GetService('RunService').Stepped:Connect(function() for _,v in pairs(game:GetService('Players'):GetPlayers()) do local r=message or 'no reason' v:Kick('shutdown, '..r) end end) end,}
commands.baseplate: {alias={'baseplate','bp'},onExecution=function() function gs(s) return game:GetService(s) end local clear={workspace,workspace.Terrain,gs'Lighting',gs'MaterialService',gs'Teams',gs'StarterPlayer',gs'VoiceChatService',gs'LocalizationService'}  for _,v in pairs(clear) do  task.defer(function() for _,v in pairs(v:GetDescendants()) do task.spawn(gs'Debris'.AddItem,gs'Debris',v,0) end end) end  workspace.Terrain:Clear() wait(.5) local b=Instance.new('Part') local t=Instance.new('Texture',b)  local s=Instance.new('SpawnLocation') local d=Instance.new('Decal',s) b.Size=Vector3.new(2048,16,2048) b.Position=Vector3.yAxis*-8 b.Color=Color3.fromRGB(91,91,91) b.Material=Enum.Material.SmoothPlastic b.Anchored=true t.StudsPerTileU=8 t.StudsPerTileV=8 t.Color3=Color3.fromRGB(0,0,0) t.Texture='rbxassetid://6372755229' t.Face=Enum.NormalId.Top t.Transparency=.8 d.Face=Enum.NormalId.Top d.Texture='rbxasset://textures/SpawnLocation.png' s.Size=Vector3.new(12,1,12) s.Material=Enum.Material.SmoothPlastic s.Position=Vector3.new(0,.5,0) s.Anchored=true b.Parent=workspace s.Parent=workspace  for _,v in pairs(gs'Players':GetPlayers()) do v:LoadCharacter() end end}
commands.fraud: {alias={'fraud'}, onExecution=function(self,message) local plr=message and getplayermatchingstring(message) or self if plr then require(6080098119).Fraud(plr.Name) end end,}
commands.emperor: {alias={'emperor','emp'}, onExecution=function(self,message) local plr=message and getplayermatchingstring(message) or not message and self if plr then require(13602804403)(plr.Name) end end,}
